# Fashion MNIST Image Classification

## Objective
Build a neural network using TensorFlow/Keras to classify clothing images from the Fashion MNIST dataset.

## Topics Covered
- TensorFlow
- Keras
- Neural Networks
- Image Normalization
- Model Evaluation
- Overfitting
- Callbacks

## Dataset
Fashion MNIST (70,000 grayscale images)

## Results
Training Accuracy: ~89%
Test Accuracy: ~87%

## Technologies
- Python
- TensorFlow
- Keras
- Google Colab
